               <msContents>
                  <summary>Book of Hours of Abba Giyorgis, መጽሐፈ፡ ሰዓታት፡ ዘአባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡; Image of the Praises of Mary, መልክአ፡ ውዳሴ፡; Asmat Prayer for Help in Memorizing; Reading from the Gospel of John 19:25-7; Ritual of Penitential Baptism, መጽሐፈ፡ ቄደር፡; Absolution of the Son, ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡;  Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡; Supplication, መስተብቁዕ; Litany, ሊጦን፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="73r" facs="009">Fols 1r–73r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3575Mashaf">Maṣḥafa
                                                  saʿātāt</title>
                     <note>with marginal notes indicating certain days of the week (Monday, <locus target="#12r">fols. 12r, </locus>; Saturday, <locus target="#18v">18v, </locus>; Sunday, <locus target="#21v">21v</locus>)‎</note>
                  </msItem>
