                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="88r" facs="096">Fols 88r and following</locus>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">, 19:25-27</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="89r" to="96v" facs="097">Fols 89r–96v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1959Mashaf">Maṣḥafa qedar</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>  መጽሐፈ፡ ቄደር፡ (ቀ)ኖና፡ ዘአንበሩ፡ መምህራን፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በእንተ፡ ዘክህደ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘአርኰሱ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
